 "remarks": "Quiet, Springdale complex tucked well off the beaten path but convenient and walkable to everything. A well designed townhouse layout with a private, attached one car garage. The main level has a comfortable entry foyer, galley kitchen that has room for a breakfast table and a sizable living room and dining room combination with sliders out to the deck that overlooks a babbling brook. Two oversized second floor bedrooms both with ample closets that share a full bath. The lower level includes the attached garage, generous rec room with walk out and full sized laundry room. This is a true handyman special being sold as is with fabulous upside potential!",
